Sarah Alexander https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Alexander 0 Sarah Alexander (née Smith; born 3 January 1971) is an English actress. She is best known for her roles in British series such as Armstrong and Miller, Smack the Pony, Coupling, The Worst Week of My Life, Green Wing, Marley's Ghosts and Jonathan Creek.
